    • PEC

      public PEC(double eta, double delta, IColony colonia, int Nu, double tau, int n)
      Public constructor for PEC simulator
      Parameters:
      eta - arithmethic parameter for pheromone evaporation event scheduling
      delta - arithmethic parameter for ant move event scheduling
      colonia - Ant Colony to which the PEC simulation refers
      Nu - Size of Colony (Ant population)
      tau - final instant for simulation, gives duration for simulation
      n - number of nodes in graph
